WEBVTT

00:00:13.680 --> 00:00:16.310 line:80%
Severe cold has invaded her body,

00:00:16.490 --> 00:00:19.420 line:80%
and it's already reached
a life-threatening stage.

00:00:20.560 --> 00:00:22.890 line:80%
She needs a scraping treatment
to stimulate her blood flow

00:00:22.890 --> 00:00:24.770 line:80%
and clear her meridians.

00:00:25.610 --> 00:00:28.920 line:80%
Is there any lady among you

00:00:29.220 --> 00:00:31.550 line:80%
who can help with the scraping treatment?

00:00:31.770 --> 00:00:32.900 line:80%
I'm her husband.

00:00:33.620 --> 00:00:34.520 line:80%
I can do it.

00:00:40.670 --> 00:00:42.730 line:80%
Wrap the blanket around her tightly.

00:00:43.110 --> 00:00:45.510 line:80%
Take off her clothes.

00:01:13.220 --> 00:01:16.750 line:80%
♪ In a lifetime of storms,
a fleeting bloom ♪

00:01:17.050 --> 00:01:19.870 line:80%
♪ The most beautiful scenery
becomes a poem ♪

00:01:20.500 --> 00:01:23.710 line:80%
♪ For a chance encounter  ♪

00:01:24.950 --> 00:01:28.670 line:80%
♪ A single letter of longing,
half a lifetime apart ♪

00:01:29.030 --> 00:01:31.270 line:80%
♪ I'll burn out my passion for you ♪

00:01:31.630 --> 00:01:35.089 line:80%
♪ Just for a glance ♪

00:01:35.440 --> 00:01:36.200 line:80%
♪ In this life ♪

00:01:36.220 --> 00:01:38.809 line:80%
♪ All that I can see or hear ♪

00:01:38.830 --> 00:01:40.460 line:80%
♪ Is that we'll live and die together ♪

00:01:40.870 --> 00:01:41.720 line:80%
♪ On this journey ♪

00:01:41.750 --> 00:01:44.540 line:80%
♪ You're all that I care about ♪

00:01:44.559 --> 00:01:46.610 line:80%
♪ My soul yearns and my dreams linger ♪

00:01:46.640 --> 00:01:47.279 line:80%
♪ After we part  ♪

00:01:47.300 --> 00:01:50.260 line:80%
♪ Where love dwells, where fear lies ♪

00:01:50.279 --> 00:01:52.610 line:80%
♪ Just one thought makes me sick ♪

00:01:52.640 --> 00:01:57.420 line:80%
♪ I wish to leave this world with you ♪

00:01:57.820 --> 00:02:01.230 line:80%
♪ We'll never be apart ♪

