00:04:42.840 --> 00:04:48.480 line:80%
[Pursuit of Jade]

00:04:48.550 --> 00:04:51.190 line:80%
[Episode 19]

00:05:08.270 --> 00:05:08.880 line:80%
Father.

00:05:11.750 --> 00:05:12.430 line:80%
Mother.

00:05:16.640 --> 00:05:20.930 line:80%
Father, Mother, where are you?

00:05:27.540 --> 00:05:28.510 line:80%
Father.

00:05:29.460 --> 00:05:30.750 line:80%
Mother.

00:05:32.670 --> 00:05:33.580 line:80%
Father!

00:05:34.240 --> 00:05:35.310 line:80%
Mother!

00:05:35.770 --> 00:05:37.370 line:80%
Wait for me!

00:05:40.709 --> 00:05:41.380 line:80%
No...

00:05:41.400 --> 00:05:42.540 line:80%
Be good, Changyu.

00:05:42.560 --> 00:05:43.230 line:80%
Go back.

00:05:43.450 --> 00:05:44.240 line:80%
Go back.

00:05:44.820 --> 00:05:46.020 line:80%
Where are you going?

00:05:46.520 --> 00:05:47.350 line:80%
Changyu.

00:05:47.810 --> 00:05:49.410 line:80%
Take good care of your sister

00:05:49.590 --> 00:05:51.060 line:80%
and yourself.

00:05:51.550 --> 00:05:52.260 line:80%
No.

00:05:52.280 --> 00:05:54.480 line:80%
Take me with you, Mother.

00:05:55.010 --> 00:05:56.320 line:80%
We've got to go.

00:05:56.640 --> 00:05:59.110 line:80%
Take me with you!

00:06:00.150 --> 00:06:01.840 line:80%
Father!

00:06:03.870 --> 00:06:05.470 line:80%
Mother!

00:06:11.960 --> 00:06:13.630 line:80%
Father!

00:06:16.370 --> 00:06:17.010 line:80%
Father.

00:06:17.730 --> 00:06:18.480 line:80%
Mother.

00:06:20.810 --> 00:06:22.340 line:80%
You're having a nightmare.

00:06:24.860 --> 00:06:25.790 line:80%
Don't be afraid.

00:06:26.600 --> 00:06:27.600 line:80%
I'm here with you.

00:06:29.670 --> 00:06:30.550 line:80%
Don't go.

00:06:33.770 --> 00:06:36.630 line:80%
I've killed many people—
my killing aura is strong.

00:06:37.790 --> 00:06:39.160 line:80%
With me here,

00:06:39.930 --> 00:06:41.660 line:80%
no ghosts would dare come near.

00:06:54.170 --> 00:06:54.900 line:80%
Wu.

00:06:55.730 --> 00:06:57.560 line:80%
Tell me, with the way
His Lordship treats her—

00:06:57.560 --> 00:07:00.760 line:80%
where you come from,
wouldn't he be expected to marry her?

00:07:00.990 --> 00:07:02.110 line:80%
I swore to keep my mouth shut.

00:07:02.110 --> 00:07:02.840 line:80%
Don't ask me.

00:07:03.350 --> 00:07:04.550 line:80%
Come on, tell me.

00:07:04.660 --> 00:07:05.590 line:80%
Tell me. Come on.

00:07:05.770 --> 00:07:06.750 line:80%
They've already gone that far.

00:07:06.750 --> 00:07:08.280 line:80%
Of course he has to marry...

00:07:08.290 --> 00:07:09.150 line:80%
Your Lordship.

00:07:09.150 --> 00:07:10.010 line:80%
Your Lordship.

00:07:13.430 --> 00:07:14.160 line:80%
Give it to me.

00:07:18.450 --> 00:07:19.380 line:80%
Your Lordshi...

00:08:29.830 --> 00:08:30.790 line:80%
Changyu.

00:08:33.790 --> 00:08:36.390 line:80%
I'll marry you, okay?

00:08:40.400 --> 00:08:41.950 line:80%
If you don't say anything,

00:08:42.990 --> 00:08:44.750 line:80%
I'll take that as a yes.

00:08:50.210 --> 00:08:50.810 line:80%
Hyah!

00:08:52.740 --> 00:08:53.460 line:80%
Whoa!

00:08:56.650 --> 00:08:59.510 line:80%
Where is His Lordship?
I have urgent news to report.

00:08:59.600 --> 00:09:01.040 line:80%
His Lordship might still be asleep.

00:09:01.040 --> 00:09:02.480 line:80%
He kept watch by that woman's bed
all night.

00:09:02.480 --> 00:09:03.330 line:80%
All night?

00:09:04.740 --> 00:09:06.330 line:80%
What's their relationship?

00:09:06.330 --> 00:09:07.260 line:80%
Asking me again?

00:09:07.390 --> 00:09:09.390 line:80%
Ask him yourself if you want to know.

00:09:14.190 --> 00:09:14.830 line:80%
What's up?

00:09:15.400 --> 00:09:16.260 line:80%
Your Lordship.

00:09:16.620 --> 00:09:17.480 line:80%
Your Lordship.

00:09:17.730 --> 00:09:19.440 line:80%
We've found the remnants of
Qingfeng Stronghold.

00:09:19.440 --> 00:09:21.440 line:80%
They were hiding in the back mountain.

00:09:21.440 --> 00:09:23.940 line:80%
Also, during interrogation last night,
the bandit who survived said

00:09:23.940 --> 00:09:26.270 line:80%
that they were bought off by Sui Yuanqing.

00:09:26.610 --> 00:09:28.160 line:80%
That bandit also said that

00:09:28.500 --> 00:09:29.510 line:80%
on the night of the massacre,

00:09:29.510 --> 00:09:33.310 line:80%
Sui Yuanqing attempted to do
something improper to that young lady.

00:09:33.560 --> 00:09:34.470 line:80%
It seemed

00:09:35.650 --> 00:09:37.650 line:80%
he was targeting her specifically.

00:09:39.570 --> 00:09:40.430 line:80%
Get the horses.

00:09:40.450 --> 00:09:42.260 line:80%
Xie Wu, Xie Qi, stay here.

00:09:42.640 --> 00:09:43.970 line:80%
The rest of the Blood-Robed Cavalry,

00:09:43.970 --> 00:09:45.050 line:80%
follow me quietly.

00:09:49.330 --> 00:09:52.150 line:80%
[Northwest Inn]

00:09:51.470 --> 00:09:53.070 line:80%
Greetings, Prime Minister.

00:09:53.470 --> 00:09:55.220 line:80%
I have arrived at the Yanzhou Barracks

00:09:55.220 --> 00:09:57.080 line:80%
and met with the Marquis of Wu'an.

00:09:57.620 --> 00:10:00.340 line:80%
Although the Marquis has doubts about
the past events in Jinzhou,

00:10:00.340 --> 00:10:02.170 line:80%
he has no solid evidence.

00:10:02.220 --> 00:10:04.350 line:80%
You can rest assured, Prime Minister.

00:10:04.390 --> 00:10:06.320 line:80%
His intentions toward you
are still unclear, Prime Minister.

00:10:06.320 --> 00:10:09.320 line:80%
I will continue to investigate
and report at any time.

00:10:09.980 --> 00:10:10.650 line:80%
Lord Sheng.

00:10:12.850 --> 00:10:13.650 line:80%
You may enter.

00:10:18.190 --> 00:10:18.880 line:80%
Lord Sheng.

00:10:19.160 --> 00:10:20.340 line:80%
The Marquis of Wu'an went to Lin'an

00:10:20.340 --> 00:10:22.130 line:80%
and wiped out Qingfeng Stronghold.

00:10:22.130 --> 00:10:25.130 line:80%
That lousy bandit den was worth him
going personally?

00:10:25.200 --> 00:10:27.670 line:80%
It was because the bandits there
had previously been incited by Sui Yuanqing

00:10:27.670 --> 00:10:28.800 line:80%
to massacre Lin'an.

00:10:29.910 --> 00:10:31.900 line:80%
That small town Lin'an.

00:10:33.840 --> 00:10:36.170 line:80%
According to
the Prime Minister's judgment,

00:10:36.170 --> 00:10:39.170 line:80%
Lord Changxin's next target
will be Lucheng.

00:10:39.980 --> 00:10:43.230 line:80%
Sui Yuanqing is his most valued son—

00:10:43.430 --> 00:10:45.900 line:80%
so why, at a time like this,
instead of reinforcing Lucheng,

00:10:45.900 --> 00:10:49.020 line:80%
would he go out of his way
to massacre such a minor town?

00:10:50.430 --> 00:10:51.680 line:80%
I do not know.

00:10:52.160 --> 00:10:54.160 line:80%
But I accidentally discovered that

00:10:54.220 --> 00:10:57.230 line:80%
while the Marquis of Wu'an was staying in Lin'an
to recover from his injuries,

00:10:57.230 --> 00:10:59.490 line:80%
he actually married into a family there.

00:11:00.520 --> 00:11:01.780 line:80%
Married into a family?

00:11:07.720 --> 00:11:08.470 line:80%
Whoa!

00:11:09.260 --> 00:11:10.020 line:80%
Whoa!

00:11:13.920 --> 00:11:16.190 line:80%
Lady Shisa...

00:11:17.110 --> 00:11:18.510 line:80%
My brother is dead.

00:11:19.420 --> 00:11:21.530 line:80%
You were the one
who led him to massacre Lin'an—

00:11:21.530 --> 00:11:23.690 line:80%
so why didn't you bring him back alive?

00:11:44.640 --> 00:11:46.160 line:80%
The Marquis of Wu'an issued a death order

00:11:46.160 --> 00:11:48.600 line:80%
to wipe out the entire
Qingfeng Stronghold.

00:11:48.600 --> 00:11:50.310 line:80%
Anyone captured would be disemboweled,

00:11:50.310 --> 00:11:51.810 line:80%
and their corpse would be left exposed
for 3 days.

00:11:51.810 --> 00:11:54.410 line:80%
He even dispatched
100 Blood-Robed Cavalry soldiers for this.

00:11:54.410 --> 00:11:57.050 line:80%
Don't you know what kind of force
100 Blood-Robed Cavalry soldiers are?

00:11:57.050 --> 00:12:00.280 line:80%
They could wipe out your Qingfeng Stronghold
100 times over!

00:12:00.280 --> 00:12:01.590 line:80%
The fact that you can still
stand here unscathed

00:12:01.590 --> 00:12:02.830 line:80%
and talk to me now

00:12:03.690 --> 00:12:05.840 line:80%
is already heaven's blessing.

00:12:11.460 --> 00:12:12.590 line:80%
So?

00:12:14.250 --> 00:12:16.910 line:80%
Am I supposed to be grateful to him
or something?

00:12:25.540 --> 00:12:26.610 line:80%
Remember this:

00:12:27.160 --> 00:12:30.490 line:80%
it was this woman named Fan Changyu
who killed your brother.

00:12:31.500 --> 00:12:33.230 line:80%
Go take your revenge yourself.

00:12:33.250 --> 00:12:34.450 line:80%
Don't come bother me.

00:12:34.920 --> 00:12:36.940 line:80%
I'll definitely flay her alive.

00:12:44.510 --> 00:12:45.180 line:80%
Wait!

00:12:50.070 --> 00:12:51.140 line:80%
Who is this kid?

00:12:52.840 --> 00:12:54.010 line:80%
Need you ask?

00:12:54.610 --> 00:12:56.190 line:80%
It must be the little bastard
that Xie Zheng had

00:12:56.190 --> 00:12:57.590 line:80%
with that butcher woman.

00:12:59.120 --> 00:13:00.410 line:80%
Little bastard?

00:13:05.940 --> 00:13:06.800 line:80%
Bring her here.

00:13:21.190 --> 00:13:22.940 line:80%
Where did you find her?

00:13:23.000 --> 00:13:24.660 line:80%
I snatched her from Xigu Lane.

00:13:25.010 --> 00:13:27.540 line:80%
I saw that her jade pendant
looked expensive,

00:13:27.890 --> 00:13:29.830 line:80%
and thought this hostage
might be worth something,

00:13:29.830 --> 00:13:31.550 line:80%
so he kept her alive.

00:13:35.490 --> 00:13:37.610 line:80%
You bet she's worth a fortune.

00:13:38.890 --> 00:13:40.290 line:80%
Let me go!

00:13:40.530 --> 00:13:41.740 line:80%
-This girl is mine now.
-Let go of me!

00:13:41.740 --> 00:13:42.950 line:80%
You villain!

00:13:42.980 --> 00:13:43.910 line:80%
I'll avenge you.

00:13:44.830 --> 00:13:46.110 line:80%
-Let go of me!
-Swear it!

00:13:46.110 --> 00:13:48.950 line:80%
That the Marquis of Wu'an
and the butcher woman will pay with their lives!

00:13:48.950 --> 00:13:51.110 line:80%
Let go of me!

00:13:54.240 --> 00:13:55.690 line:80%
I swear.

00:13:55.920 --> 00:13:57.920 line:80%
Let me go!

00:13:59.010 --> 00:14:01.140 line:80%
You'll have to pay with your life, too.

00:14:03.050 --> 00:14:06.700 line:80%
[Government]

00:14:09.730 --> 00:14:10.330 line:80%
My Lord.

00:14:10.860 --> 00:14:13.370 line:80%
Over 500 bodies were recovered
in Lin'an Town,

00:14:13.370 --> 00:14:14.880 line:80%
and countless were injured.

00:14:14.880 --> 00:14:16.490 line:80%
Over 100 houses were damaged,

00:14:16.490 --> 00:14:19.670 line:80%
and the townspeople are still short of
food and clothing.

00:14:19.670 --> 00:14:21.800 line:80%
Notify the Jizhou Granary
and Weaving Bureau

00:14:21.800 --> 00:14:23.880 line:80%
to urgently allocate supplies
to support Lin'an.

00:14:23.880 --> 00:14:25.560 line:80%
Provide shelter for
the homeless women and children

00:14:25.560 --> 00:14:27.250 line:80%
at the Jizhou Prefecture posthouse.

00:14:27.250 --> 00:14:27.890 line:80%
Also,

00:14:28.330 --> 00:14:31.130 line:80%
bring some wood
from the neighboring counties...

00:14:31.740 --> 00:14:33.680 line:80%
My Lord, your health comes first.

00:14:33.700 --> 00:14:36.460 line:80%
You haven't recovered from
your serious injuries yet...

00:14:36.460 --> 00:14:38.320 line:80%
If I hadn't left Lin'an back then,

00:14:39.690 --> 00:14:42.290 line:80%
perhaps this tragedy
wouldn't have happened.

00:14:44.500 --> 00:14:46.100 line:80%
Who could have predicted it?

00:14:48.030 --> 00:14:50.090 line:80%
You needn't blame yourself, My Lord.

00:14:50.380 --> 00:14:51.260 line:80%
Report!

00:14:54.050 --> 00:14:56.250 line:80%
My Lord, we've found traces of Mrs. Fan.

00:14:59.540 --> 00:15:01.140 line:80%
Do as I ordered immediately.

00:15:01.160 --> 00:15:02.360 line:80%
-Yes.
-Assemble some troops and follow me.

00:15:02.360 --> 00:15:03.220 line:80%
-Yes.
-My Lord.

00:15:03.760 --> 00:15:04.760 line:80%
You haven't fully recovered.

00:15:04.760 --> 00:15:05.760 line:80%
I can go instead.

00:15:06.340 --> 00:15:07.500 line:80%
I promised Master.

00:15:07.530 --> 00:15:09.100 line:80%
I must go in person for this.

00:15:09.130 --> 00:15:09.730 line:80%
My Lord!

00:15:48.550 --> 00:15:51.480 line:80%
The Jizhou Army has been searching
in our direction.

00:15:51.590 --> 00:15:54.450 line:80%
Our men at the pass
can't hold them back much longer.

00:15:55.880 --> 00:15:57.870 line:80%
So why is it that
we can't let Li Huai'an's men

00:15:57.870 --> 00:15:58.710 line:80%
find us?

00:15:59.680 --> 00:16:00.970 line:80%
Why so many questions?

00:16:01.000 --> 00:16:02.520 line:80%
Go ask Master if you dare.

00:16:04.370 --> 00:16:05.730 line:80%
Fake soldiers?

00:16:06.590 --> 00:16:10.590 line:80%
They're probably in league with
the bandits from Qingfeng Stronghold.

00:16:17.350 --> 00:16:18.810 line:80%
Ma'am, what's the matter?

00:16:20.010 --> 00:16:21.500 line:80%
Your Young Madam's clothes

00:16:21.500 --> 00:16:23.530 line:80%
she wore yesterday
when she was all sweaty...

00:16:23.530 --> 00:16:24.200 line:80%
Young Madam?

00:16:24.200 --> 00:16:27.120 line:80%
I've washed and dried them for her.

00:16:29.490 --> 00:16:30.290 line:80%
Thank you for your trouble.

00:16:30.290 --> 00:16:31.380 line:80%
You may go in.

00:17:00.980 --> 00:17:02.560 line:80%
Good girl.

00:17:03.360 --> 00:17:05.760 line:80%
Your fever is finally gone.

00:17:22.919 --> 00:17:23.760 line:80%
Ma'am.

00:17:24.869 --> 00:17:26.310 line:80%
You saved me.

00:17:26.700 --> 00:17:28.380 line:80%
Poor girl.

00:17:28.950 --> 00:17:30.500 line:80%
You ran into bandits

00:17:30.530 --> 00:17:32.080 line:80%
and caught a chill.

00:17:32.470 --> 00:17:34.520 line:80%
You've suffered greatly.

00:17:34.890 --> 00:17:38.180 line:80%
Luckily, you have a good husband.

00:17:39.070 --> 00:17:40.400 line:80%
They are all villains.

00:17:40.430 --> 00:17:41.830 line:80%
None of them is my husband.

00:17:41.830 --> 00:17:43.070 line:80%
Villains?

00:17:44.900 --> 00:17:45.900 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:17:46.390 --> 00:17:48.120 line:80%
Let's get out of here together.

00:17:49.480 --> 00:17:50.070 line:80%
But...

00:17:51.330 --> 00:17:52.170 line:80%
Young lady,

00:17:52.200 --> 00:17:54.760 line:80%
this old body of mine
can't possibly keep up.

00:18:00.800 --> 00:18:01.460 line:80%
Young lady,

00:18:01.630 --> 00:18:03.480 line:80%
where are you taking me?

00:18:03.500 --> 00:18:04.480 line:80%
Young lady...

00:18:11.040 --> 00:18:11.820 line:80%
The back mountain.

00:18:11.820 --> 00:18:12.430 line:80%
Let's go.

00:18:27.040 --> 00:18:27.910 line:80%
They're gone.

00:18:28.470 --> 00:18:29.390 line:80%
Follow me.

00:19:03.740 --> 00:19:04.670 line:80%
Come on, Ma'am.

00:19:04.690 --> 00:19:05.880 line:80%
Come on. Be careful.

00:19:07.000 --> 00:19:09.200 line:80%
Why are there suddenly
so many troops here?

00:19:09.200 --> 00:19:10.310 line:80%
Come on, Ma'am.

00:19:11.880 --> 00:19:13.930 line:80%
Ma'am, just hide here.

00:19:13.950 --> 00:19:15.010 line:80%
I'll go take a look.

00:19:15.070 --> 00:19:16.380 line:80%
If they really are government officials,

00:19:16.380 --> 00:19:17.570 line:80%
I'll come back and get you.

00:19:17.570 --> 00:19:20.570 line:80%
Young lady, please be extra careful.

00:19:20.970 --> 00:19:21.760 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:19:40.440 --> 00:19:41.680 line:80%
Lord Li!

00:19:43.520 --> 00:19:45.240 line:80%
Lord Li!

00:19:47.200 --> 00:19:48.350 line:80%
Lord Li!

00:19:50.720 --> 00:19:51.960 line:80%
Lord Li!

00:19:53.040 --> 00:19:54.260 line:80%
Lord Li!

00:20:27.140 --> 00:20:29.070 line:80%
Do you really have to go to such lengths
just to catch me?

00:20:29.070 --> 00:20:30.200 line:80%
Just for this thing,

00:20:30.200 --> 00:20:31.160 line:80%
you even risked your life!

00:20:31.160 --> 00:20:32.160 line:80%
Is it really that important?

00:20:32.160 --> 00:20:33.690 line:80%
It's none of your business!

00:20:41.750 --> 00:20:42.870 line:80%
Let me go!

00:20:42.900 --> 00:20:44.850 line:80%
Is this thing really that important
to you?

00:20:44.850 --> 00:20:46.290 line:80%
Who gave it to you?

00:20:49.460 --> 00:20:50.180 line:80%
A friend.

00:20:51.160 --> 00:20:53.460 line:80%
Friend? What kind of friend?

00:20:53.630 --> 00:20:55.250 line:80%
What does it have to do with you?

00:20:55.250 --> 00:20:58.050 line:80%
What kind of friend is worth
risking your life for?

00:20:58.400 --> 00:20:59.660 line:80%
None of your business!

00:21:00.170 --> 00:21:01.190 line:80%
Just kill me if you want.

00:21:01.190 --> 00:21:02.120 line:80%
Enough talk!

00:21:45.680 --> 00:21:48.550 line:80%
Never mind. As long as you are safe.

00:21:55.450 --> 00:21:56.060 line:80%
Whoa!

00:21:56.290 --> 00:21:56.850 line:80%
Whoa!

00:22:00.780 --> 00:22:01.890 line:80%
I finally found you.

00:22:01.890 --> 00:22:04.200 line:80%
I heard your voice
at the foot of the mountain just now.

00:22:04.200 --> 00:22:05.600 line:80%
Was someone chasing you?

00:22:07.460 --> 00:22:09.060 line:80%
Why are you so badly injured?

00:22:09.760 --> 00:22:11.760 line:80%
I'm okay. Just some scratches.

00:22:12.400 --> 00:22:13.760 line:80%
There's a blind old lady

00:22:13.790 --> 00:22:15.120 line:80%
who escaped with me.

00:22:15.140 --> 00:22:16.020 line:80%
She's hiding in the grass

00:22:16.020 --> 00:22:18.290 line:80%
along this mountain path further up.

00:22:18.640 --> 00:22:19.710 line:80%
Lord Li, please

00:22:19.740 --> 00:22:21.400 line:80%
have someone take care of her.

00:22:22.030 --> 00:22:23.620 line:80%
Just tell her you're government officials,

00:22:23.620 --> 00:22:24.880 line:80%
so she won't be scared.

00:22:25.020 --> 00:22:25.550 line:80%
Zhuoran.

00:22:25.860 --> 00:22:26.340 line:80%
Yes.

00:22:26.920 --> 00:22:27.930 line:80%
You four, follow me.

00:22:27.930 --> 00:22:28.560 line:80%
Yes.

00:22:31.590 --> 00:22:33.590 line:80%
Are the villagers of Xigu Lane okay?

00:22:56.960 --> 00:22:57.960 line:80%
Mr. Li.

00:23:02.200 --> 00:23:03.330 line:80%
Mr. Li...

00:23:37.670 --> 00:23:38.860 line:80%
Mrs. Yin.

00:23:42.760 --> 00:23:44.130 line:80%
Mrs. Yin...

00:23:46.000 --> 00:23:47.480 line:80%
Mrs. Yin...

00:24:26.000 --> 00:24:27.790 line:80%
One, two, three!

00:24:27.110 --> 00:24:29.060 line:80%
[Xigu Lane]

00:24:29.840 --> 00:24:30.800 line:80%
Move aside!

00:24:33.760 --> 00:24:34.760 line:80%
Who are you?

00:24:34.070 --> 00:24:35.390 line:80%
[Xigu Lane]

00:24:34.760 --> 00:24:35.800 line:80%
Go away. Move.

00:24:36.310 --> 00:24:37.070 line:80%
Hurry up and get the work done.

00:24:37.070 --> 00:24:37.870 line:80%
His Lordship has instructed

00:24:37.870 --> 00:24:38.830 line:80%
to cremate them as soon as possible

00:24:38.830 --> 00:24:39.870 line:80%
to prevent a plague.

00:24:39.870 --> 00:24:41.070 line:80%
Listen up, everyone.

00:24:41.660 --> 00:24:42.290 line:80%
My Lord.

00:24:42.930 --> 00:24:45.200 line:80%
They were human beings. Be gentle.

00:24:45.220 --> 00:24:46.240 line:80%
Yes, My Lord.

00:24:47.390 --> 00:24:48.700 line:80%
Be gentle, everyone.

00:24:49.550 --> 00:24:50.680 line:80%
-Yes.
-Understood.

00:24:58.660 --> 00:25:00.760 line:80%
[Xigu Lane]

00:25:15.010 --> 00:25:16.660 line:80%
-Mrs. Zhao...
-Changyu!

00:25:56.750 --> 00:26:00.940 line:80%
[Xigu Lane]

00:26:12.530 --> 00:26:13.660 line:80%
Where is Changning?

00:26:18.170 --> 00:26:19.040 line:80%
Changning...

00:26:22.150 --> 00:26:23.710 line:80%
Changning is missing.

00:26:34.940 --> 00:26:35.700 line:80%
Changyu!

00:26:51.000 --> 00:26:52.260 line:80%
Let's have a rest here.

00:26:52.760 --> 00:26:54.360 line:80%
Go find some food over there.

00:26:54.760 --> 00:26:55.280 line:80%
Okay.

00:26:55.360 --> 00:26:56.040 line:80%
-Got it.
-Let's go.

00:26:56.040 --> 00:26:56.760 line:80%
That way.

00:27:03.780 --> 00:27:04.900 line:80%
Stop crying!

00:27:11.570 --> 00:27:12.630 line:80%
If you keep crying,

00:27:12.960 --> 00:27:14.770 line:80%
I'll throw you into the river.

00:27:19.720 --> 00:27:20.330 line:80%
Go

00:27:21.100 --> 00:27:22.630 line:80%
and get me some clean water.

00:27:23.930 --> 00:27:24.610 line:80%
Go!

00:27:40.630 --> 00:27:41.520 line:80%
Kid.

00:27:42.630 --> 00:27:43.350 line:80%
Kid.

00:27:47.070 --> 00:27:48.680 line:80%
I knew you'd be scared.

00:27:49.320 --> 00:27:50.760 line:80%
Look how cute it is.

00:27:50.780 --> 00:27:51.630 line:80%
Touch it.

00:27:51.920 --> 00:27:53.360 line:80%
Look at its eyes.

00:27:55.440 --> 00:27:57.000 line:80%
Don't you have any shame?

00:27:57.350 --> 00:27:58.960 line:80%
If you're so tough,
go fight the Marquis of Wu'an.

00:27:58.960 --> 00:28:01.890 line:80%
Bullying a little girl
doesn't make you a hero, okay?

00:28:03.690 --> 00:28:05.170 line:80%
Why are you so serious?

00:28:05.780 --> 00:28:06.890 line:80%
I was just joking.

00:28:15.980 --> 00:28:17.260 line:80%
Oh no. She has asthma.

00:28:19.800 --> 00:28:22.610 line:80%
How did the Marquis of Wu'an
sire such a sickly child?

00:28:22.610 --> 00:28:23.610 line:80%
So troublesome.

00:28:23.640 --> 00:28:24.270 line:80%
Shut up.

00:28:26.370 --> 00:28:27.970 line:80%
There's no medicine in here.

00:28:28.680 --> 00:28:29.790 line:80%
It's okay.

00:28:33.220 --> 00:28:35.150 line:80%
I also had asthma when I was little.

00:28:36.820 --> 00:28:39.400 line:80%
Relax. You'll feel better soon.

00:28:42.300 --> 00:28:44.430 line:80%
I didn't expect you to know this trick.

00:28:51.580 --> 00:28:52.140 line:80%
Fine.

00:28:53.810 --> 00:28:55.610 line:80%
I'll leave this kid in your care.

00:28:56.330 --> 00:28:58.090 line:80%
Don't let her die on the way.

00:29:03.000 --> 00:29:04.770 line:80%
Thank you, Miss.

00:29:10.800 --> 00:29:14.590 line:80%
[Sui]

00:29:18.420 --> 00:29:19.390 line:80%
Why?

00:29:21.060 --> 00:29:23.550 line:80%
Why can't you just listen to me?

00:29:29.290 --> 00:29:32.000 line:80%
I meant for you to be dressed
in splendid clothes,

00:29:32.000 --> 00:29:33.660 line:80%
adorned with gold and jewels,

00:29:33.940 --> 00:29:35.900 line:80%
looking radiant by my side.

00:29:36.480 --> 00:29:37.840 line:80%
And yet these fine clothes

00:29:37.840 --> 00:29:39.430 line:80%
do not please you?

00:29:40.270 --> 00:29:41.530 line:80%
Bring the tailor here.

00:29:43.410 --> 00:29:44.860 line:80%
Drag the tailor out

00:29:45.200 --> 00:29:46.310 line:80%
and snap her hands.

00:29:46.620 --> 00:29:48.680 line:80%
-Yes.
-Master, please spare my life!

00:29:48.910 --> 00:29:50.710 line:80%
Master, please spare me!

00:29:54.440 --> 00:29:56.280 line:80%
Such rare treasures

00:29:56.530 --> 00:29:58.380 line:80%
and dazzling objects—

00:29:58.760 --> 00:30:01.360 line:80%
yet you show absolutely
no affection for them.

00:30:02.710 --> 00:30:03.590 line:80%
Guards!

00:30:03.670 --> 00:30:05.140 line:80%
This craftswoman has poor taste.

00:30:05.140 --> 00:30:07.130 line:80%
Drag her out and gouge out her eyes!

00:30:07.150 --> 00:30:07.460 line:80%
Yes.

00:30:07.490 --> 00:30:09.110 line:80%
Master, please spare my life!

00:30:09.110 --> 00:30:10.680 line:80%
-Move.
-Please spare my life, Master!

00:30:10.680 --> 00:30:11.640 line:80%
Please spare me!

00:30:13.420 --> 00:30:15.630 line:80%
This cook can't even make
anything you like.

00:30:15.630 --> 00:30:17.380 line:80%
Then there's no need for him
to keep his tongue.

00:30:17.380 --> 00:30:18.620 line:80%
Master, please spare me!

00:30:18.620 --> 00:30:19.550 line:80%
Enough!

00:30:31.020 --> 00:30:32.380 line:80%
You madman.

00:30:33.660 --> 00:30:35.590 line:80%
If I had known it would come to this,

00:30:36.350 --> 00:30:38.040 line:80%
I never would have saved you.

00:30:39.020 --> 00:30:40.490 line:80%
You're just a madman!

00:30:43.000 --> 00:30:44.410 line:80%
I'm a madman?

00:30:45.730 --> 00:30:47.340 line:80%
I treat you so well,

00:30:48.290 --> 00:30:49.620 line:80%
and you call me a madman?

00:30:50.600 --> 00:30:52.670 line:80%
Then why can't you just do as I wish

00:30:52.700 --> 00:30:54.310 line:80%
and go mad with me?

00:30:56.570 --> 00:30:57.890 line:80%
Those people outside

00:30:58.280 --> 00:31:00.110 line:80%
all died because of you.

00:31:01.100 --> 00:31:02.540 line:80%
If you want to make me obey

00:31:03.300 --> 00:31:05.700 line:80%
by threatening the lives of your servants,

00:31:06.250 --> 00:31:08.010 line:80%
it will only cost more lives.

00:31:10.490 --> 00:31:12.410 line:80%
Stop hurting innocent people.

00:31:14.410 --> 00:31:16.000 line:80%
Why don't you do as I wish

00:31:17.830 --> 00:31:18.550 line:80%
and kill me?

00:31:23.400 --> 00:31:24.990 line:80%
You know perfectly well—

00:31:25.010 --> 00:31:26.480 line:80%
you can act so recklessly

00:31:26.500 --> 00:31:28.470 line:80%
only because of

00:31:28.500 --> 00:31:30.500 line:80%
the little affection I have for you.

00:31:32.660 --> 00:31:33.290 line:80%
Fine.

00:31:35.590 --> 00:31:37.490 line:80%
Bring that little brat here.

00:31:45.090 --> 00:31:45.910 line:80%
Mother!

00:31:50.940 --> 00:31:52.620 line:80%
You may not care about

00:31:53.630 --> 00:31:55.070 line:80%
the lives of others.

00:31:55.860 --> 00:31:57.540 line:80%
But I see this brat

00:31:57.570 --> 00:31:59.200 line:80%
looks so innocent and kind.

00:32:01.310 --> 00:32:03.800 line:80%
Can you really harden your heart

00:32:03.920 --> 00:32:05.330 line:80%
and abandon him?

00:32:10.430 --> 00:32:12.340 line:80%
If you want to do it, do it now.

00:32:13.780 --> 00:32:15.600 line:80%
He's your son anyway.

00:32:16.490 --> 00:32:19.090 line:80%
He shouldn't have been born
in the first place.

00:32:19.450 --> 00:32:20.960 line:80%
Kill him first,

00:32:21.600 --> 00:32:23.090 line:80%
and then kill me.

00:32:27.240 --> 00:32:28.680 line:80%
My son?

00:32:31.000 --> 00:32:32.160 line:80%
If

00:32:33.720 --> 00:32:36.040 line:80%
I could really bring myself to kill him,

00:32:37.000 --> 00:32:38.500 line:80%
what would you do then?

00:32:44.690 --> 00:32:45.910 line:80%
Do as you please.

00:32:47.260 --> 00:32:49.390 line:80%
I'll just pretend I never had this son.

00:32:50.370 --> 00:32:51.620 line:80%
I've long had enough.

00:32:53.460 --> 00:32:54.790 line:80%
Mother...

00:32:57.370 --> 00:32:58.620 line:80%
I think you

00:32:59.470 --> 00:33:01.670 line:80%
still haven't understood what I meant.

00:33:02.460 --> 00:33:05.600 line:80%
I am the one
who wants to kill him the most.

00:33:07.810 --> 00:33:11.220 line:80%
Do you dare to bet that I won't?

00:33:25.930 --> 00:33:26.860 line:80%
Don't!

00:33:29.000 --> 00:33:29.850 line:80%
You win.

00:33:30.920 --> 00:33:31.840 line:80%
You win.

00:33:34.630 --> 00:33:35.550 line:80%
You win.

00:33:36.910 --> 00:33:38.850 line:80%
I beg you, don't kill him.

00:33:50.490 --> 00:33:51.240 line:80%
How is it?

00:34:09.959 --> 00:34:10.800 line:80%
Do I look good?

00:34:26.510 --> 00:34:27.160 line:80%
Enough.

00:34:28.530 --> 00:34:29.170 line:80%
Enough.

00:34:31.080 --> 00:34:31.939 line:80%
This is enough.

00:34:33.130 --> 00:34:33.800 line:80%
Mother.

00:34:38.800 --> 00:34:40.390 line:80%
My family of three

00:34:40.670 --> 00:34:42.100 line:80%
is finally reunited.

00:34:47.910 --> 00:34:48.830 line:80%
Take him away.

00:34:48.830 --> 00:34:49.430 line:80%
Yes.

00:34:51.010 --> 00:34:52.209 line:80%
-Mother!
-Bao'er...

00:34:52.350 --> 00:34:53.310 line:80%
Mother!

00:34:53.760 --> 00:34:55.390 line:80%
Bao'er, don't be afraid!

00:34:55.910 --> 00:34:57.250 line:80%
Mother!

00:34:58.020 --> 00:34:59.370 line:80%
I finally know

00:34:59.530 --> 00:35:01.210 line:80%
where your weakness lies.

00:35:38.890 --> 00:35:39.700 line:80%
My Lord.

00:35:40.570 --> 00:35:41.840 line:80%
What brings you here?

00:35:42.360 --> 00:35:43.140 line:80%
Come on.

00:35:43.150 --> 00:35:44.420 line:80%
Please come in and have a seat.

00:35:44.420 --> 00:35:45.480 line:80%
No need, Mrs. Zhao.

00:35:46.440 --> 00:35:48.320 line:80%
We're here to tell Mrs. Fan

00:35:51.720 --> 00:35:53.380 line:80%
that we've found her father's

00:35:53.690 --> 00:35:55.490 line:80%
and Fan Daniu's wife's corpses.

00:35:58.100 --> 00:35:59.580 line:80%
They're dead too?

00:36:07.210 --> 00:36:08.140 line:80%
My Lord,

00:36:08.920 --> 00:36:11.360 line:80%
could you not tell Changyu this for now?

00:36:12.010 --> 00:36:14.210 line:80%
I'm worried she can't handle this much.

00:36:15.040 --> 00:36:15.640 line:80%
Okay.

00:36:16.720 --> 00:36:17.970 line:80%
Where is Mrs. Fan now?

00:36:23.190 --> 00:36:25.540 line:80%
Changyu looks fine on the surface,

00:36:25.610 --> 00:36:27.270 line:80%
eating and drinking as usual.

00:36:27.370 --> 00:36:28.700 line:80%
But I know deep down

00:36:28.850 --> 00:36:31.430 line:80%
that she's suffering in silence.

00:36:32.100 --> 00:36:33.960 line:80%
Mrs. Fan is truly strong-willed.

00:36:34.640 --> 00:36:36.840 line:80%
She can stay so calm in such a situation.

00:36:37.190 --> 00:36:38.470 line:80%
No wonder on the day of the massacre,

00:36:38.470 --> 00:36:39.950 line:80%
she managed to fight her way in and out
multiple times,

00:36:39.950 --> 00:36:41.410 line:80%
saving so many villagers.

00:36:41.670 --> 00:36:43.600 line:80%
I just hope she doesn't break down.

00:36:47.760 --> 00:36:48.470 line:80%
Changyu.

00:36:52.970 --> 00:36:53.970 line:80%
Changyu?

00:37:11.630 --> 00:37:20.270 line:80%
[In Memory of Late Father Fan Erniu
and Late Mother Meng Lihua, Interred Together]

00:37:32.430 --> 00:37:33.310 line:80%
Changyu!

00:37:35.670 --> 00:37:36.630 line:80%
Give it to me.

00:37:38.020 --> 00:37:39.940 line:80%
The government will handle these things.

00:37:39.940 --> 00:37:41.680 line:80%
Why do it yourself?

00:37:45.240 --> 00:37:46.320 line:80%
The dead are gone.

00:37:47.180 --> 00:37:48.960 line:80%
Don't wear yourself out.

00:37:53.420 --> 00:37:58.480 line:80%
[Tomb of Lady Kang San]

00:37:55.010 --> 00:37:57.260 line:80%
Granny Kang had been all alone.

00:37:58.870 --> 00:38:00.870 line:80%
Two generations of men in her family

00:38:01.950 --> 00:38:03.550 line:80%
all died on the battlefield.

00:38:04.300 --> 00:38:05.980 line:80%
Her grandson, Xiaohu,

00:38:07.710 --> 00:38:09.570 line:80%
is still looking for his grandma.

00:38:10.660 --> 00:38:12.320 line:80%
She also had an older grandson

00:38:13.540 --> 00:38:15.540 line:80%
who went for corvee labor years ago,

00:38:16.530 --> 00:38:18.730 line:80%
and his whereabouts are still unknown.

00:38:23.110 --> 00:38:24.770 line:80%
Mrs. Yin from the noodle shop—

00:38:25.590 --> 00:38:26.920 line:80%
she came from Anhua.

00:38:27.610 --> 00:38:28.940 line:80%
I need to write a letter

00:38:30.050 --> 00:38:31.250 line:80%
to inform her family.

00:38:38.250 --> 00:38:40.750 line:80%
[Tomb of Chef Li Deqin]

00:38:38.560 --> 00:38:40.560 line:80%
Chef Li from Yixiang Restaurant—

00:38:41.740 --> 00:38:43.260 line:80%
his father is already 70

00:38:43.970 --> 00:38:45.630 line:80%
and still working on the farm.

00:38:46.760 --> 00:38:49.090 line:80%
I don't know if he survived this disaster.

00:38:50.500 --> 00:38:52.360 line:80%
I have to find time to check on him.

00:38:56.340 --> 00:38:57.770 line:80%
And Mr. Wang—

00:38:58.770 --> 00:39:01.370 line:80%
he treated the magistrate's office
like home.

00:39:04.530 --> 00:39:06.510 line:80%
And the other neighbors...

00:39:10.830 --> 00:39:12.640 line:80%
If I don't put them in coffins,

00:39:13.560 --> 00:39:15.100 line:80%
I won't be at peace.

00:39:16.350 --> 00:39:17.390 line:80%
You've been going without sleep or rest.

00:39:17.390 --> 00:39:18.920 line:80%
How could your body take it?

00:39:20.440 --> 00:39:21.750 line:80%
Let me take you to rest for a while.

00:39:21.750 --> 00:39:22.450 line:80%
Let's go.

00:39:22.760 --> 00:39:24.280 line:80%
I dare not rest.

00:39:25.870 --> 00:39:27.800 line:80%
I see them as soon as I close my eyes.

00:39:29.750 --> 00:39:31.280 line:80%
Every single one of them...

00:39:36.660 --> 00:39:38.420 line:80%
And my Changning...

00:39:42.490 --> 00:39:43.570 line:80%
Changyu.

00:39:43.730 --> 00:39:47.070 line:80%
Changning wasn't among the bodies
we found.

00:39:46.920 --> 00:39:50.770 line:80%
[In Memory of Late Father Fan Erniu
and Late Mother Meng Lihua, Interred Together]

00:39:47.160 --> 00:39:48.910 line:80%
She's lucky and resilient.

00:39:48.930 --> 00:39:50.700 line:80%
I'm sure she'll be fine.

00:39:53.650 --> 00:39:54.450 line:80%
Don't worry.

00:39:55.590 --> 00:39:57.850 line:80%
I've sent more men to search everywhere.

00:39:58.470 --> 00:39:59.640 line:80%
She'll be fine.

